txt.en: Gortheron the Doom-caller threw down the gauntlet, and you rose to the challenge. He has been vanquished at the height of his power.
Gortheron has been defeated at the height of his power
Gortheron the Doom-caller threw down the gauntlet, and you rose to the challenge. He has been vanquished at the height of his power.
Gortheron, the leader of the Gaunt-lords and servant of Sauron, has been defeated by your hand when he was at the peak of his reign and power.
